<pb ed="T" id="T19.0931.0072c" n="0072c"/>
<lb n="0072c01"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0072c02"/><head type="no">No. 931</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0072c03"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0072046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本，【甲】建長四年寫東寺三密藏本，【乙】三十帖策子第十七帖，【丙】黃檗版淨嚴等加筆本</note>金剛頂經觀自在王如來修行法
<lb n="0072c04"/><note n="0072047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一卷〕－【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0072047"><lem>一卷</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0072c05"/>
<lb n="0072c06"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0072048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（開府…門）四十一字＝（唐北天竺三藏沙門大廣智）十一字【明】【丙】，（大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智）十一字【甲】，〔開府…譯〕四十六字－【乙】</note><note n="0072048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅國公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑒正號大廣智大興善寺三藏沙門不空奉詔譯〕四十六字－【乙】，（開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅國公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑒正號大廣智大興善寺三藏沙門）四十一字＝（唐北天竺三藏沙門大廣智）十一字【明】【丙】，（開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅國公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑒正號大廣智大興善寺三藏沙門）四十一字＝（大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智）十一字【甲】</note><app n="0072048"><lem>開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅國
<lb n="0072c07"/>公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑒
<lb n="0072c08"/>正號大廣智大興善寺三藏沙門
<lb n="0072c09"/>不空奉　詔譯</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">唐北天竺三藏沙門大廣智不空奉詔譯</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智不空奉詔譯</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0072c10"/><p>我今依金剛頂經。演金剛蓮花達<note n="0072049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">摩＝磨【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0072049"><lem>摩</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">磨</rdg></app>法要。先
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0931.0073a" n="0073a"/>
<lb n="0073a01"/>須入於灌頂三昧耶曼<note n="0073001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">茶＝荼【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】＊</note><app n="0073001"><lem>茶</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">荼</rdg></app>羅。發大菩提心。捨
<lb n="0073a02"/>身命財饒益一切。勇猛精進隨念相應。慈悲
<lb n="0073a03"/>喜捨無有間斷。如是之人方應修習。其曼<app type="＊" source="0073001"><lem>茶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">荼</rdg></app>
<lb n="0073a04"/>羅畫像等法<note n="0073002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔廣〕－【甲】，廣＝應【乙】</note><app n="0073002"><lem>廣</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">應</rdg></app>如餘經所說。凡入精舍欲念
<lb n="0073a05"/>誦時。先以五輪著地。頂禮<note n="0073003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（大）＋本【乙】</note><app n="0073003"><lem>本</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">大本</rdg></app>尊觀自在王
<lb n="0073a06"/>如來。次禮北方不空成就如來乃至無動寶
<lb n="0073a07"/>生遍照如來。悉皆依法至誠敬禮。雙膝而跪
<lb n="0073a08"/>蓮花合掌。懺悔三業一切過咎</p>
<lb n="0073a09"/><lg><l>我從無量劫</l><l>淪滯生死海</l>
<lb n="0073a10"/><l>今以清淨心</l><l>發露而悔過</l>
<lb n="0073a11"/><l>如諸佛所懺</l><l>我今亦如是</l>
<lb n="0073a12"/><l>願我及眾生</l><l>一切皆清淨</l></lg>
<lb n="0073a13"/><p>密<note n="0073004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（真）＋言【乙】</note><app n="0073004"><lem>言</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">真言</rdg></app>曰</p>
<lb n="0073a14"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>馺&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>婆<note place="inline"><note n="0073005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">去＋（聲）【明】【丙】＊</note><app n="0073005"><lem>去</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">去聲</rdg></app></note>&CB00085;秝<note place="inline"><note n="0073006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">入＋（聲）【明】【丙】＊</note><app n="0073006"><lem>入</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">入聲</rdg></app></note>陀<note n="0073007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二〕－【甲】</note><app n="0073007"><lem><note place="inline">二</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>薩&CB00085;達<app type="＊" source="0072049"><lem>摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">磨</rdg></app>
<lb n="0073a15"/><note place="inline"><note n="0073008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三＝二【明】【丙】</note><app n="0073008"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">二</rdg></app></note><note n="0073009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">馺＝薩【明】【丙】</note><app n="0073009"><lem>馺</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">薩</rdg></app>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>婆<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0073005"><lem>去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【丙】">去聲</rdg></app></note>&CB00085;<note place="inline">四</note>秝<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0073006"><lem>入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【丙】">入聲</rdg></app></note>度<note n="0073010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">澸＝憾【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0073010"><lem>澸</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">憾</rdg></app><note n="0073011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔五〕－【明】</note><app n="0073011"><lem><note place="inline">五</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0073a16"/><p>次應隨喜過現未來諸佛菩薩所集福智</p>
<lb n="0073a17"/><lg><l><note n="0073012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">過去乃至喜二十字明乙丙三本俱作長行</note><note n="0073012" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="a"/>過去乃至喜二十字明乙丙三本俱作長行</note>過<note n="0073013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">去＝現【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0073013"><lem>去</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">現</rdg></app>三世<note n="0073014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">佛＝諸【乙】</note><app n="0073014"><lem>佛</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">諸</rdg></app></l><l>菩薩與眾生</l>
<lb n="0073a18"/><l>所集諸善根</l><l>合掌盡隨喜</l></lg>
<lb n="0073a19"/><p>次應右膝著地。虛心合掌置於頂上。想禮諸
<lb n="0073a20"/>佛如來及菩薩足。誦密<note n="0073015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（真）＋言【丙】</note><app n="0073015"><lem>言</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">真言</rdg></app>曰</p>
<lb n="0073a21"/><p type="dharani">唵&CB00425;納摩<note place="inline"><note n="0073016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二合上＝上聲二合【明】【丙】</note><app n="0073016"><lem>二合上</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">上聲二合</rdg></app></note>尾多<note place="inline">多字半音與尾字合呼</note></p>
<lb n="0073a22"/><p>禮諸佛已。依座<note n="0073017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">印＋（坐或半跏全跏隨意）【甲】</note><app n="0073017"><lem>印</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">印坐或半跏全跏隨意</rdg></app>而坐入定思惟。觀無<note n="0073018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">量＋（壽）【甲】</note><app n="0073018"><lem>量</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">量壽</rdg></app>
<lb n="0073a23"/>如來周遍法界。行者己身悉在彼會。然後結
<lb n="0073a24"/><note n="0073019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔祕〕－【明】</note><app n="0073019"><lem>祕</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>密三昧耶印。堅固縛以檀慧禪智。相合而
<lb n="0073a25"/><note n="0073020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00594;＝堅【乙】</note><app n="0073020"><lem>&CB00594;</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">堅</rdg></app>。以此驚覺聖眾。誦密言曰</p>
<lb n="0073a26"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合二</note><note n="0073021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">跛＝跋【明】＊</note><app n="0073021"><lem>跛</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">跋</rdg></app>娜&CB00757;<note place="inline">二合三</note>三昧耶<note n="0073022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔四〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0073022"><lem><note place="inline">四</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>薩
<lb n="0073a27"/>怛梵<note place="inline"><note n="0073023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔三合〕－【明】</note><app n="0073023"><lem>三合</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>五</note></p><p place="inline">次應結一切如來歡喜<note n="0073024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔悅〕－【明】</note><app n="0073024"><lem>悅</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>意三昧
<lb n="0073a28"/>耶印。准前印唯以忍願入<note n="0073025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔掌〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0073025"><lem>掌</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0073026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">中＋（右押左指面相著誦）【甲】</note><app n="0073026"><lem>中</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">中右押左指面相著誦</rdg></app>。密言曰</p>
<lb n="0073a29"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>三<note n="0073027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00757;＝昧【明】【丙】</note><app n="0073027"><lem>&CB00757;</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">昧</rdg></app>耶<note n="0073028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">呼＝吽&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0073028"><lem>呼</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">吽</rdg></app><note place="inline">引二</note>蘇<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0073005"><lem>去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【丙】">去聲</rdg></app></note>囉多<note place="inline">三</note>薩怛梵
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0931.0073b" n="0073b"/>
<lb n="0073b01"/><note n="0073029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔三合四〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0073029"><lem><note place="inline">三合四</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0073b02"/><p>次結開心<note n="0073030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔印〕－【明】＊</note><app n="0073030"><lem>印</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。觀二乳上有怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>吒字。以
<lb n="0073b03"/>金剛縛。三拍開之。密言曰</p>
<lb n="0073b04"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合二</note>滿馱<note place="inline">三</note>怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>吒<note place="inline">四</note></p>
<lb n="0073b05"/><p>次結入智字印。於<note n="0073031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔己〕－【明】</note><app n="0073031"><lem>己</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>面前。觀一紅蓮華上有
<lb n="0073b06"/><note n="0073032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">娑＝惡【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0073032"><lem>娑</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">惡</rdg></app>字。以堅固縛禪智入中。進力相拄。想捻
<lb n="0073b07"/>其字內<note n="0073033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔於〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0073033"><lem>於</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>心中。誦密言曰</p>
<lb n="0073b08"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合引</note>吠捨<note place="inline">二</note>惡<note n="0073034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔三〕－【明】【甲】【乙】＊，【丙】</note><app n="0073034"><lem><note place="inline">三</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0073b09"/><p>次結闔智字印。不易前<app type="＊" source="0073030"><lem>印</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>。進力拄禪智背。
<lb n="0073b10"/>想闔心門。密言曰</p>
<lb n="0073b11"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合二</note>母瑟<note n="0073035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">致＝知【甲】，智【乙】</note><note n="0073035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">致＝知【甲】，＝智【乙】</note><app n="0073035"><lem>致</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">知</rdg><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">智</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合<anchor id="fxT19p0073b02"/>三</note>&CB00805;<note n="0073036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔四〕－【明】＊</note><note n="0073036" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="＊"/>〔四〕－【明】＊</note><app n="0073036"><lem><note place="inline">四</note></lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0073b12"/><p>次結辟除結界印。戒方右押左外相<note n="0073037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">交＝刃【甲】，又【乙】</note><note n="0073037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">交＝刃【甲】，＝又【乙】</note><app n="0073037"><lem>交</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">刃</rdg><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">又</rdg></app>。忍願
<lb n="0073b13"/>相拄。以進力鉤戒方。禪智捻檀慧頭。密言
<lb n="0073b14"/>曰</p>
<lb n="0073b15"/><p type="dharani">唵<note n="0073038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一〕－【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0073038"><lem><note place="inline">一</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>阿密栗<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0073039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00418;＝都【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0073039"><lem>&CB00418;</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">都</rdg></app>娜婆<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二</note>吽<note place="inline">三</note>泮吒
<lb n="0073b16"/><note place="inline"><note n="0073040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔吒半音呼之〕－【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0073040"><lem>吒半音呼之</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>四</note></p>
<lb n="0073b17"/><p>以此印左轉三匝。辟除不善。右旋三匝。隨意
<lb n="0073b18"/>遠近以為結界</p>
<lb n="0073b19"/><p>次結三摩地印。二羽<note n="0073041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">仰＋（相）【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0073041"><lem>仰</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">仰相</rdg></app><note n="0073042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">叉＝又【乙】</note><app n="0073042"><lem>叉</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">又</rdg></app>。進力相背而&CB00594;。
<lb n="0073b20"/>禪智捻進力頭。置於跏上。誦密言曰</p>
<lb n="0073b21"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>三<note n="0073043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">麼＝摩【明】【丙】＊</note><app n="0073043"><lem>麼</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">摩</rdg></app><note place="inline">引</note>地<note place="inline">二</note>&CB00425;娜<note n="0073044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">名＝銘【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0073044"><lem>名</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">銘</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合三</note>頡哩<note place="inline">二合<note n="0073045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">引＋（四）【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0073045"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">引四</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0073b22"/><p>其出入息一一明了。<note n="0073046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">觀＋（察）【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0073046"><lem>觀</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">觀察</rdg></app>虛空中無量諸佛。一
<lb n="0073b23"/>時彈指警覺行者而告之言。汝今云何成無
<lb n="0073b24"/>上覺。不知諸佛實相法要。行者爾時聞警覺
<lb n="0073b25"/>已。<note n="0073047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（即）＋白【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0073047"><lem>白</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">即白</rdg></app>佛言云何名真實。唯願如來為我解
<lb n="0073b26"/>說。爾時諸佛告行者言。善哉善哉能作是問。
<lb n="0073b27"/><note n="0073048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">汝＝淨【明】</note><app n="0073048"><lem>汝</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">淨</rdg></app>想心中所內惡字瑩徹於心。誦密言曰</p>
<lb n="0073b28"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>唧多&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底<note place="inline">二</note>味<note n="0073049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鄧＋（徒&CB00040;反）夾註【丙】</note><app n="0073049"><lem>鄧</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">鄧<note place="inline">徒&CB00040;反</note></rdg></app>迦<note n="0073050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00080;＝嚕【明】【丙】，路【甲】</note><note n="0073050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00080;＝嚕【明】【丙】，＝路【甲】</note><app n="0073050"><lem>&CB00080;</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">嚕</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">路</rdg></app>弭<note place="inline">三</note></p>
<lb n="0073b29"/><p>當默誦一遍。便想為月輪。如在輕霧</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0931.0073c" n="0073c"/>
<lb n="0073c01"/><p>為欲令其月輪得清淨故。誦此密言曰</p>
<lb n="0073c02"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>冒地唧多母怛<app type="＊" source="0073021"><lem>跛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">跋</rdg></app><note place="inline">二<note n="0073051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二〕－【乙】＊</note><app n="0073051"><lem>二</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note>娜夜<note n="0073052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">弭＋（三）夾註【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0073052"><lem>弭</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">弭<note place="inline">三</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0073c03"/><p><note n="0073053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">誦＋（此）【丙】</note><app n="0073053"><lem>誦</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">誦此</rdg></app>已諦觀心月極令清淨。如處<note n="0073054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大＝太【明】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0073054"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">太</rdg></app>虛廓無
<lb n="0073c04"/>瑕翳。復於<note n="0073055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">心月＝月中【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0073055"><lem>心月</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">月中</rdg></app><note n="0073056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（中）＋想【丙】</note><app n="0073056"><lem>想</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">中想</rdg></app>一蓮華。誦密言曰</p>
<lb n="0073c05"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>底瑟<note n="0073057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吒＝&CB00109;【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0073057"><lem>吒</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&CB00109;</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合二</note>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合三</note>&CB00425;娜麼<note place="inline">二合四</note></p>
<lb n="0073c06"/><note n="0073058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔想其…四〕四十二字－【明】</note><app n="0073058" word-count="42"><lem><p>想其蓮花與月。漸漸而引周遍法界。量等虛
<lb n="0073c07"/>空。誦密言曰</p>
<lb n="0073c08"/><p type="dharani">唵<app type="＊" source="0073038"><lem><note place="inline">一</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app>薩頗<note n="0073059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二合囉二＝羅二合【甲】</note><app n="0073059"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0073060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔囉二〕－【乙】</note><app n="0073060"><lem>囉<note place="inline">二</note></lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">羅二合</note></rdg></app>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合<note n="0073061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔三〕－【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0073061"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note>&CB00425;娜麼<note place="inline">二合
<lb n="0073c09"/>四</note></p></lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0073c10"/><p>其引蓮華中放無量光。隨光流出無量無邊
<lb n="0073c11"/>際極樂世界。一一世界妙寶莊嚴。皆有觀自
<lb n="0073c12"/>在王如來。<note n="0073062" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">與＋（諸）【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0073062"><lem>與</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">與諸</rdg></app>聖眾前後圍遶。如是觀已漸斂
<lb n="0073c13"/>其蓮華。誦密言曰</p>
<lb n="0073c14"/><p type="dharani">唵<app type="＊" source="0073038"><lem><note place="inline">一</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app>僧賀囉<note place="inline"><note n="0073063" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二合〕－【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0073063"><lem>二合</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>二</note>&CB00425;娜麼<note place="inline">二合三</note></p>
<lb n="0073c15"/><p>如是一切世界諸佛如來。隨華而斂量等本
<lb n="0073c16"/>身。即變己身為無量壽佛身。紅<note n="0073064" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">頗梨＝玻&CB00226;【明】【丙】</note><app n="0073064"><lem>頗梨</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">玻&CB00226;</rdg></app>色放大
<lb n="0073c17"/>光明。結三<app type="＊" source="0073043"><lem>麼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【丙】">摩</rdg></app>地<note n="0073065" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">印＋（坐）【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0073065"><lem>印</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">印坐</rdg></app>金剛蓮華<note n="0073066" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔座〕－【乙】</note><app n="0073066"><lem>座</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。想行者己
<lb n="0073c18"/>身為如來已。復恐散亂而有退失。次作加持
<lb n="0073c19"/>印而加持之。堅固縛以進力屈如<note n="0073067" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蓮＋（花）【甲】</note><app n="0073067"><lem>蓮</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">蓮花</rdg></app>葉。禪智
<lb n="0073c20"/>並&CB00594;<note n="0073068" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔印〕－【甲】</note><app n="0073068"><lem>印</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>心額喉頂隨所<note n="0073069" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">印＋（處）【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0073069"><lem>印</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">印處</rdg></app>。想頡哩<note place="inline">二合</note>字。誦
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0931.0074a" n="0074a"/>
<lb n="0074a01"/>密言曰</p>
<lb n="0074a02"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合<app type="＊" source="0073051"><lem>二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app></note>達麼<note place="inline"><note n="0074001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三＝二【乙】</note><app n="0074001"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">二</rdg></app></note>頡哩<note place="inline">二<note n="0074002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">合＋（四）【丙】</note><app n="0074002"><lem>合</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">合四</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0074a03"/><p>次結灌頂印。蓮華合掌進力相蹙如<note n="0074003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">寶＋（珍）【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0074003"><lem>寶</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">寶珍</rdg></app>。檀慧
<lb n="0074a04"/>&CB00594;相遠。置於額<note n="0074004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">上＋（誦）【甲】</note><app n="0074004"><lem>上</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">上誦</rdg></app>。密言曰</p>
<lb n="0074a05"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>&CB00425;娜麼<note place="inline">二合二</note>囉怛那<note place="inline">二合引<note n="0074005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三＝二【甲】</note><app n="0074005"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">二</rdg></app></note>毘<note n="0074006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">詵＝訖【乙】</note><app n="0074006"><lem>詵</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">訖</rdg></app>遮<note place="inline">四</note>薩
<lb n="0074a06"/><note n="0074007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00085;＋（二合）【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0074007"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&CB00085;二合</rdg></app>&CB00805;<note place="inline">五</note>頡哩<note place="inline">二合六</note>怛<note n="0074008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00080;＝洛【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0074008"><lem>&CB00080;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">洛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合七</note></p>
<lb n="0074a07"/><p>次結蓮華鬘印。以前印從額分手。繞至頂後。
<lb n="0074a08"/>結蓮華拳。如繫華<note n="0074009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔鬘〕－【乙】</note><app n="0074009"><lem>鬘</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>勢。徐徐前下散誦密言
<lb n="0074a09"/>曰</p>
<lb n="0074a10"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>&CB00425;娜麼<note place="inline">二合二</note>囉怛那<note place="inline">二合三</note>麼<note n="0074010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0074010"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>&CB00619;<note n="0074011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔四〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0074011"><lem><note place="inline">四</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>&CB00805;
<lb n="0074a11"/><note place="inline"><note n="0074012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔牟含反〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0074012"><lem>牟含<note n="0074013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">反＝切【明】【丙】＊</note><app n="0074013"><lem>反</lem><rdg wit="【明】【丙】" resp="Taisho">切</rdg></app></lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>五</note></p>
<lb n="0074a12"/><p>次結甲冑印。結蓮華拳。前後繞身如擐甲法。
<lb n="0074a13"/>誦密言曰</p>
<lb n="0074a14"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>阿婆耶<note place="inline">二</note>&CB00425;娜麼<note place="inline">二合三</note>迦<note n="0074014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00085;＝縛【甲】</note><app n="0074014"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">縛</rdg></app>制<note place="inline">四</note>滿馱
<lb n="0074a15"/><note n="0074015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔五〕－【甲】</note><app n="0074015"><lem><note place="inline">五</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>囉乞灑<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00805;<note place="inline">六</note>吽<note place="inline">七</note>憾<note place="inline">八</note></p>
<lb n="0074a16"/><p>次結歡喜印。蓮華合掌微拍三聲。誦密言曰</p>
<lb n="0074a17"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>&CB00425;娜麼<note place="inline">二合二</note>&CB00418;使野<note place="inline">二<note n="0074016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">合＋（三）【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0074016"><lem>合</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">合三</rdg></app></note>護<note place="inline">引<app type="＊" source="0073061"><lem>三</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app></note></p>
