<lb n="0074c03"/><p>次結蓮華外四供養燒香印。蓮華合掌下散。
<lb n="0074c04"/>猶如焚<note n="0074062" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">香＋（勢）【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0074062"><lem>香</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">香勢</rdg></app>。誦密言曰</p>
<lb n="0074c05"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>&CB00425;娜麼<note place="inline">二合<app type="＊" source="0074053"><lem>二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app></note>度閉<note n="0074063" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二合三〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0074063"><lem><note place="inline">二合三</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0074064" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">噁＝惡【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0074064"><lem>噁</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">惡</rdg></app><note place="inline">四</note></p>
<lb n="0074c06"/><p>次結蓮華散華印。蓮華合掌前上散。猶如散
<lb n="0074c07"/>華勢。誦密言曰</p>
<lb n="0074c08"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>&CB00425;娜麼<note place="inline">二合<app type="＊" source="0074053"><lem>二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app></note><note n="0074065" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔補〕－【乙】</note><app n="0074065"><lem>補</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>瑟閉<note place="inline">二合三</note>唵<app type="＊" source="0074024"><lem><note place="inline">四</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0074c09"/><note n="0074066" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔次結…四〕三十三字－【乙】</note><app n="0074066" word-count="33"><lem><p>次結蓮華燈印。蓮華合掌禪智&CB00594;相逼。誦密
<lb n="0074c10"/>言曰</p>
<lb n="0074c11"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>&CB00425;娜麼<note place="inline">二合二</note>&CB00135;<note place="inline">引</note>閉<note place="inline">三</note>&CB00135;<app type="＊" source="0074024"><lem><note place="inline">四</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></p></lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0074c12"/><p>次結蓮華塗香印。十度作蓮華合掌。當心分
<lb n="0074c13"/>散。如塗<note n="0074067" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔香〕－【乙】</note><app n="0074067"><lem>香</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>勢。誦密言曰</p>
<lb n="0074c14"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>&CB00425;娜麼<note place="inline">二合二</note><note n="0074068" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（母伽…百）百十七字∞（&CB03306;提…曰）百三十六字【乙】，&CB03306;＝喭【明】【丙】，獻【甲】，&CB03306;三【乙】</note><note n="0074068" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="a"/>（母伽…百）百十七字∞（&CB03306;提…曰）百三十六字【乙】，&CB03306;＝喭【明】【丙】，獻【甲】，&CB03306;三【乙】</note>&CB03306;提<app type="＊" source="0073061"><lem><note place="inline">三</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app>虐<app type="＊" source="0074024"><lem><note place="inline">四</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0074c15"/><p>次結根本印。堅固縛以忍願相拄。如<note n="0074069" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蓮＋（花）【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0074069"><lem>蓮</lem><rdg wit="【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">蓮花</rdg></app>葉
<lb n="0074c16"/>形。誦密言曰</p>
<lb n="0074c17"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>路計<note n="0074070" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">什＝濕【丙】</note><app n="0074070"><lem>什</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">濕</rdg></app>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>囉<app type="＊" source="0074053"><lem><note place="inline">二</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app>囉<note n="0074071" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【丙】</note><app n="0074071"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>惹<note place="inline"><note n="0074072" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三＝二【甲】</note><app n="0074072"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">二</rdg></app></note>頡哩
<lb n="0074c18"/><note place="inline">二合四</note></p>
<lb n="0074c19"/><p>結根本印。誦明七遍已。然後執蓮子珠。相應
<lb n="0074c20"/>念誦。於四時中隨力而作。若欲止時。重結根
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0931.0075a" n="0075a"/>
<lb n="0075a01"/>本印復誦七遍根本陀羅<note n="0075001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">尼＋（於頂上散於）【甲】</note><app n="0075001"><lem>尼</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">尼於頂上散於</rdg></app>。次結八供養
<lb n="0075a02"/><note n="0075002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔印〕－【乙】</note><app n="0075002"><lem>印</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。然後發遣<note n="0075003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">本尊＝聖眾次【甲】，聖眾【乙】</note><note n="0075003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">本尊＝聖眾次【甲】，＝聖眾【乙】</note><app n="0075003"><lem>本尊</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">聖眾次</rdg><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">聖眾</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0075a03"/><p>發遣印。以前根本印。從臍<note n="0075004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">至面＝上至頂上【甲】，至頂上【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0075004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">至面＝上至頂上【甲】，＝至頂上【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0075004"><lem>至面</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">上至頂上</rdg><rdg wit="【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">至頂上</rdg></app>方散。合掌
<lb n="0075a04"/>於頂上。想觀自在王如來復還本宮。誦密言
<lb n="0075a05"/>曰</p>
<lb n="0075a06"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">一</note>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合二</note>&CB00425;娜麼<note place="inline">二合三</note>穆<app type="＊" source="0074024"><lem><note place="inline">四</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0075a07"/><p>發遣本尊已。隨意發願。復以<note n="0075005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">甲＋（胄）【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0075005"><lem>甲</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">甲胄</rdg></app>印護身。以
<lb n="0075a08"/>馬頭明王結界印。左<note n="0075006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">旋＋（一匝）【甲】</note><app n="0075006"><lem>旋</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">旋一匝</rdg></app>解<note n="0075007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">界＋（對聖眾發露懺悔禮佛出道場）【甲】</note><app n="0075007"><lem>界</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">界對聖眾發露懺悔禮佛出道場</rdg></app>。隨意<note n="0075008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＝結【甲】</note><app n="0075008"><lem>經</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">結</rdg></app>行往
<lb n="0075a09"/>諸淨處。讀大乘<note n="0075009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔大〕－【甲】</note><app n="0075009"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>般若經華嚴涅槃及楞伽
<lb n="0075a10"/>等經。行住坐臥常念本尊無令間斷</p>
<lb n="0075a11"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead><note n="0075010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（金剛…法）十三字＝（阿彌陀瑜伽略念誦法）九字【甲】，（阿彌陀佛念誦法）七字【乙】</note><note n="0075010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（金剛…法）十三字＝（阿彌陀瑜伽略念誦法）九字【甲】，＝（阿彌陀佛念誦法）七字【乙】</note><app n="0075010" word-count="13"><lem>金剛頂經觀自在王如來修行法</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">阿彌陀瑜伽略念誦法</rdg><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">阿彌陀佛念誦法</rdg></app><note n="0075011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">甲本奧書云建長四年壬子五月十五日之寫了一交了，丙本附錄并奧書云施不動尊殘食真言　曩莫糝滿多&CB00085;日囉二合南引怛洛二合引吒阿慕伽戰拏摩賀嚕灑拏娑破二合吒野吽怛洛二合麼野怛洛二合麼野吽怛羅二合吒憾引&CB00805;引每欲喫食，　色色咸加持三遍，於淨處或石上，安置，不動尊聖者常加護其人，除一切災難口舌，所為所作依本心如意，常隨逐其人皆得成就，寫本云請成身院經藏本比校移點了　件記云是傳寫三十帖之本也云云，貞享元甲子九月十五日以和本一校了并訓點之淨嚴四十八，元祿十六年二月一日以淨嚴和上之本再挍了尊敬</note></jhead></juan></div1>
